channel.title: TestScape Problem
channel.description: I'm using the most recent testscape. I've recently made a server with it on, the only modification is that the items that you start with are different, steel arrows, dragonstone ring, ghostly shirt and skirt, ghostly gloves, wizard boots, unholy book, and whip. Yet, when i join the server, and anybody else does, they die and lose everything they start off with, before the black screen goes away. Does anybody know how to solve this? Any help would be appreciated.
